messages.content: Hi there! Thanks for calling EZ Mobile Mechanic. What’s going on with your vehicle today?
well good question um well today my car it won't start
Got it! Can you tell me the year, make, and model of your car?
Thanks! So, just to confirm, your 1995 Suburban won't start. Is there anything specific you noticed before it stopped working?
yeah it would make this clicking noise
Sounds like it could be a battery issue or something similar. Would you like me to text you a quick estimate for the diagnostic?
